<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4660703>
    dc:description "Figs 1-7. 1, Zinza grandis head. 2, Z. grandis epandrium, sursty!us, cercus. 3, Z. grandis hypandrium, phallus, ejaculatory apodeme. 4, Z. grandis wing. 5, Cairnsimyia sydneiensis D. McAlpine scutellum. 6, Neorhinotora aristalis (Fischer) scutellum. 7, Z. grandis scutellum. Abbreviation: gst, gonostylus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4660703/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4660707>
